{"tid":2337201,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"戴祖儀買勞力士當聖誕禮物送畀自己 網上炒至35萬元！","createTime":"2020-12-23T06:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T10:52:31.000Z","uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06c4bbcb696989b2954adf3996b7f90b7951579b","tid":2337201,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:40:59.000Z","msg":"戴祖儀向來都是給人一種「富二代」的感覺，不時大曬限量玩具figure，又專登租兩個場來放玩具，而日前，她就在個人社交網上載兩張相片，細看之下，原來她購買了勞力士ROLEX Day-Date系列Day-Date 36，難怪她自己都開心表示：「買到心頭好Yeah」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPzUPnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPzUPnd.jpg&h=3b824416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴祖儀昨日（16/12）於個人Instagram上載了兩張相片，並留言表示：「Early Xmas gift to myself Ref18238 1995 same age ƪ(&hearts;ﻬ&hearts;)ʃ #買到心頭好Yeah #差咁d手毛添 #今年唔買野lu #感謝營養不良的錢包」。<br />\n<br />\n根據戴祖儀所示的Reference No及年份，原來是勞力士ROLEX Day-Date系列的Day-Date 36 Ref 18238，於1995年出產，亦是戴祖儀的出生年份，而按勞力士官方資料所示，戴祖儀手上的Day-Date 36現時價值15萬，而同系列手錶的全金加鑽官方訂價為約28萬，網上還有人炒至35萬至100不等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnE5V2k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnE5V2k.png&h=7fcb89fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了名錶之外，戴祖儀最熱愛的就是收藏限量玩具figure，還分別租兩個場來放玩具，一個是用來放Hot Toys，另一個剛用來放藝術成份較高且價錢偏貴的玩具及藝術品，如日本藝術家空山基 Sorayama 限量500隻的滑浪機器人，戴祖儀早兩年前就以1700美金入手，現時就已升值8倍，價值約10萬港元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Fqdkt6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Fqdkt6.png&h=9b9a48f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n較早前，戴祖儀與日本藝術家橋爪悠也（Yuya）合作舉辦藝術展覽，橋爪悠也更以Joey為創作藍本，設計出卡通畫及Figure等，其中價值五位數的1:1等身Figure，雖然一度被海關扣押審查，未能在展覽中展示，後來Figure終於成功出關，Joey還親自迎接這個Figure的到來！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6rj0um.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6rj0um.png&h=64e20f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n Joey表示好榮幸可以成為Yuya老師筆下的角色，她笑言： 「個人偶細緻到連我面上粒癦都有！而且佢知我好鍾意音樂，所以特登襯番個木結他同好多音符畀我。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tid2YfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTid2YfU.jpg&h=ce932d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JdhLbAV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdhLbAV.png&h=085989f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nmplus.hk/watch/戴祖儀-勞力士-聖誕禮物-759157/5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Fwatch%2F%E6%88%B4%E7%A5%96%E5%84%80-%E5%8B%9E%E5%8A%9B%E5%A3%AB-%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E7%A6%AE%E7%89%A9-759157%2F5%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=912031c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nmplus.hk/watch/戴祖儀-勞力士-聖誕禮物-759157/5/</a>"},{"pid":"9979338d6672dae8635f9af983eb67c0fc3246a8","tid":2337201,"uid":247211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"daydate有幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb2aa81d2ebae7bb4853036274cd1b74f897294","tid":2337201,"uid":1991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"35萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為冰藍..."},{"pid":"cda3d921d87e98831578c17be3ba9a20d04cd2e5","tid":2337201,"uid":251333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢屋企係做咩架"},{"pid":"3369f44797b353a511b0641d2b8f9cbc9bd6310c","tid":2337201,"uid":25260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cda3d921d87e98831578c17be3ba9a20d04cd2e5","tid":2337201,"uid":251333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢屋企係做咩架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"扑野"},{"pid":"933b45e8373da34ba120e49512eb1151da770346","tid":2337201,"uid":137080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"前排見完佢買左隻 而家又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass